{
  "stem": "21786.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And it was called Theresienstadt, T-H-E-R-I-E-N-S-T-A-D-T or Terezin into Czech, T-E-R-E-Z-I-N, which was a fortress, military fortress, with huge walls and a moat around it and two gates, main gates into it.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the Czechs, they kept it pretty well-preserved.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there was a small town in the middle of the fortress, inhabitants about 7,000.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And there were about four huge military barracks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There was the military, Czech military was located there, I think originally whether it was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] just plain air forces.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I don't know exactly what kind of part of military.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But altogether, there were about 7,000 soldiers there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the Germans conceived the idea that they would evacuate this thing which-- and they will put Czech gendarmes as guards around it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And it will be very easy, simply, to put there a large quantity of Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And it was very, relatively easy to guard it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they started to send, first, people who are preparing this kind of move.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They evacuated the Czechs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no  military, naturally, there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the-- that place which had space for about 11,000 people and soldiers in the peak of its production had about 77,000 Jews in it, pretty overcrowded.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that became kind of a sifting station.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "From there, they were sending then Jews, again, to the east, to Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We, somehow, when the transportation started-- I'm skipping many things-- when the transportation started we knew that something very, very-- I will repeat the name-- odious is happening.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For there was naturally a blackout on the news.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we received occasionally a postcard from a camp, like from Sehelmn, S-E-H-E-L-M-N on which was written-- I'm translating, I'm well off.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I am healthy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'm-- we came here on this and this date.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
